The menu is already open as indicated by the focused state of the 'STORES' link and the visible submenu with options like 'All Stores', 'Configuration', etc. Looking at the accessibility tree, I can see that element [614] contains a link to 'All Stores' which would be the main entry point to the Stores section. I should click on this link to navigate to the Stores section.
